title: Draft Recap - Round 1
itunes:title: Draft Recap - Round 1
description:
Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys talk about the first few picks in the 2020 NFL Draft. After that, Bucky and Rhett discuss the quarterbacks picked in the first round (4:53) and react to the Packers taking Utah State QB Jordan Love (8:03). Then, the pair give their favorite picks of Round 1 (16:05) and also the most surprising picks from the night (22:45). To wrap up the show, the duo look ahead to Day 2 of the draft (33:55).
